---

ðŸ§± 1. HTML (Structure)

This is your main layout â€” pages, buttons, product containers, etc. Save this as index.html.

<!-- index.html -->
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
